videos.description: Bogdan Bogdanovic's floater hits the top of the backboard before falling for the first points of the game.

videos.headline: Bogdanovic hits the top of the backboard on opening bucket

videos.description: Joel Embiid is falling out of bounds and throws the ball near the rim where Ben Simmons dunks it home.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Pass or shot? Embiid throws it near the rim where Simmons flushes it home) 2021/06/11 ESHEET

videos.headline: Pass or shot? Embiid throws it near the rim where Simmons flushes it home

videos.description: Dwight Howard flips in the missed shot right before the first-quarter buzzer goes off.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Dwight Howard beats the first-quarter buzzer) 2021/06/11 ESHEET

videos.headline: Dwight Howard beats the first-quarter buzzer

videos.description: Trae Young shows off the vision lobbing it up to John Collins for the dunk.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Trae throws pinpoint lob to Collins for the jam) 2021/06/11 ESHEET

videos.headline: Trae throws pinpoint lob to Collins for the jam

videos.description: John Collins soars towards the rim for his second alley-oop dunk of the second quarter.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Young to Collins connection works again) 2021/06/11 ESHEET

videos.headline: Young to Collins connection works again

videos.description: Trae Young goes right down the lane and flips in the layup right before the first-half buzzer sounds.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (76ers don't stop ball, Trae Young gets easy layup to end the half) 2021/06/11 ESHEET

videos.headline: 76ers don't stop ball, Trae Young gets easy layup to end the half

videos.description: Danny Green limps off the court after suffering a calf injury, he wouldn't return to the game.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Danny Green leaves the game with calf injury) 2021/06/11 ESHEET

videos.headline: Danny Green leaves the game with calf injury

videos.description: Seth Curry goes down the lane and flips in the sweet hook shot forcing the Hawks to take a timeout.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Seth Curry puts in sweet hook shot) 2021/06/11 ESHEET

videos.headline: Seth Curry puts in sweet hook shot

videos.description: The Hawks forget to cover Ben Simmons leading to the monster transition dunk. Then later, Ben Simmons lobs it to Joel Embiid for the emphatic jam.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Simmons, Embiid put on dunk show in the third) 2021/06/11 ESHEET

videos.headline: Simmons, Embiid put on dunk show in the third

videos.description: Joel Embiid denies Onyeka Okongwu on one end, then comes back and grabs the offensive rebound for the dunk on the other.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Embiid doing it on defense and offense) 2021/06/11 ESHEET

videos.headline: Embiid doing it on defense and offense

videos.description: After Dwight Howard misses badly on the 3-point attempt it ends up with George Hill who splashes the jumper.

videos.headline: Dwight Howard very off on 3-point attempt, but George Hill is on the mark

videos.description: Trae Young wants Ben Simmons to shoot free throws after fouling him then he trolls the ref by telling him to open his eyes after a call.
